<placeName cert="high" full="yes">?</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>τῷ κυρίῳ μου <choice><corr>θεοσεβεῖ</corr><sic>θεωσεβη</sic></choice> Ἄπα <choice><corr>Ἰωάννῃ</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>ωανην</sic></choice> Λεῦχις <choice><corr>Μαλάμου</corr><sic>μαλαμος</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="2"/>ἡ <choice><corr>χρηστότης</corr><sic>χρηστωτητα</sic></choice> σου κατέλαβεν πάντας τοὺς <choice><corr>μὴ</corr><sic>μυ</sic></choice> δυναμένους· 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἐμὲ</corr><sic><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear>αμε</sic></choice> <choice><corr>φθάσῃ</corr><sic>φ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">θ</unclear>ασι</sic></choice> ἡ <choice><corr>ἐλεημοσύνην</corr><sic><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ελε</unclear>ημωσυ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>ην</sic></choice> σου, κύριε. μετὰ <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic>των</sic></choice> Θεὸν 

    <lb n="4"/>τὴν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ὴν <choice><corr>βοήθειαν</corr><sic>β<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ηθιαν</sic></choice> <choice><corr>προσδοκῶ</corr><sic>προσδωκω</sic></choice>, <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να <choice><corr>ἀξιώσῃς</corr><sic>αξι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ωσις</unclear></sic></choice> <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic>των</sic></choice> τρι-

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>βοῦνον</corr><sic>τριβουν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ων</unclear></sic></choice> <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>ων</sic></choice> Γοῦνθον καὶ ἄρῃ αὐτὰς ἀπὸ τῆς οἰκίας 

    <lb n="6"/>μου, <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> χήρα γυνή εἰμι. κύριέ μου, διὰ <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic>των</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Θεὸν</corr><sic>θεων</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ποίει</corr><sic>πυει</sic></choice>. </ab></div><div n="meta.35415" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.35415" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="376" notAfter="400">spätes IV (?)</date></p></div><div n="meta.35415" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört vielleicht zum Archiv des Apa Johannes. Zum Ort und zur Datierung vgl. BL X, S. 85 mit BASP 32, 1995, S. 190 -  192 .</p></div><div n="meta.35415" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Herm.</title><biblScope type="numbers">17</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">35415</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0134</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">17</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0134;;17" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.35415" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">86</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.35415" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.35415" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en" default="NO"